        <h2>Solution&colon; What needs to be done first&quest;</h2>
        <h3>Empathize</h3>
        <p>Translating my character analysis skills&comma; I sought to observe and understand user&apos;s expectations before&comma; during&comma; and after choosing to pay for a digital subscription service&period;</p>
        <h4>Secondary Research&colon; Outlining Expectations</h4>
        <p>I compared PsyHealth&apos;s user journeys with competitors and <span class="bolded">suggested merging the Settings and Profile screens</span>&period;</p>
        <p>Combining the administrative details into one screen reduces clicks&comma; making it easier for users to edit their information for a better experience while meeting expectations&period;</p>
