        <h3>Ideate&comma; Test&comma; Iterate&colon; Why this change&quest;</h3>
        <p>Feedback on my low&dash;fidelity wireframes revealed <span class="bolded">layouts depend on content context</span>&period; The mid&dash;fidelity wireframes with accurate copy led to iterations to the monthly and annual subscription plan placements&period;</p>
        <p>Through A&sol;B testing to streamline user focus on payment decisions&comma; having two options helped my team&apos;s decision&dash;making and support for faster development&period;</p>
